{"tid":1005324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HR的主要工作⋯","createTime":"2019-02-02T06:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T06:35:44.000Z","uid":215980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e563643b2e8afa1bd323eced04888505db82d217","tid":1005324,"uid":215980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"人稱HR的human resources，人力資源部門主要為公司管理人物、物力、資源以提升及推動公司最大效益。人力資源管理工作包括：工作分析；制定人力需求計劃以及人員招募；培訓及開發；薪酬及福利管理、績效評估；勞動關係管理等。所謂節省公司資源，就是員工有開工無糧出。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拖糧仆街死全家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef324bb461771d0fc1b7f06f7ce45c3d6453a7f","tid":1005324,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你去勞工署囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你攪得一頭半個月先再出比你條乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}